          <actionDate>2018-11-15</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Estate Tax Rate Reduction Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to reduce the rate for the tax on estates, gifts, and generation-skipping transfers to 20%. (Under current law, the highest rate is 40%.) </p> <p>The bill also exempts the budgetary effects of the tax reduction from the Pay-As-You-Go (PAYGO) rules established by the Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010 and the FY2018 congressional budget resolution.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
